data.description: Sprawling 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch in Grand Blanc Schools! This home features an enormous sun-drenched family room with vaulted ceilings and sliding door to the outdoor living space. Perfect for hosting holiday gatherings. The kitchen has sightlines through to the large dining room and into the family room, with views of the private, treed yard. The basement is framed and partially drywalled, has a lot of natural light, and has been recently waterproofed. Easily finish for additional living space! Store yard equipment in the attached, one car garage, and still have room to park! Or park in the paved driveway, with turnaround. You’ll like the privacy of the dead-end road and you’ll LOVE the convenience, just minutes from everything!
